com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Class BusinessPartnerService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.BusinessPartnerService

  • public class BusinessPartnerService
extends Object

    This service enables you to create, read, update, and delete Business Partners, Suppliers, and Customers in SAP S/4HANA system.

    Business Documentation

    Details:

    OData Service: API_BUSINESS_PARTNER
    API Version: 1
    Minimum ERP Version: 1708
    Communication Scenario: Business Partner, Customer and Supplier Integration (SAP_COM_0008)
    Scope Items: Master Data Integration (1RO)
